  " - Exposed SillyTavern operation → RunSlashCommand",
  " - JS object inspection / complex filtering / frontend method → RunJavaScriptApi",
  " - Unknown structure → inspect first, narrow later; do not guess ctx.xxx.yyy.zzz",
